ğŸš€ Digital Clock & Weather Dashboard
A sleek, neon-themed digital clock built with Vanilla JavaScript. This project serves as a functional dashboard widget that provides real-time timekeeping, date display, and live weather updates.

ğŸŒŸ Features
Real-time Clock: Displays hours, minutes, and seconds.

Toggleable Format: Switch between 12-hour (AM/PM) and 24-hour modes.

Persistent Settings: Remembers your preferred time format even after refreshing the page using localStorage.

Live Weather: Fetches current temperature and weather conditions via the OpenWeatherMap API.

Dynamic Date: Automatically updates the day and month.

Responsive Design: Centered, dark-mode aesthetic that looks great on any screen.

ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack
HTML5: Structure and semantics.

CSS3: Flexbox layout and neon glow effects.

JavaScript (ES6+): DOM manipulation, Async/Await for API calls, and State Management.

